Frequently Asked Questions

Is an internet connection required to process PDFs?
No. The application is designed to function entirely offline. All processing happens locally on your Mac or iPad to ensure document confidentiality.

Where do my stamped or sanitised files go?
When you click "Apply & Export" or "Compile PDF", the app will open a standard system dialog asking you where you would like to save the newly generated file. It does not overwrite your original files.

How do I reorder files in the document queue?
You can click and drag any file or section divider in the list to rearrange the compilation order before stamping.

Does the app support both Mac and iPad?
Yes. The application is a universal purchase and supports cross-platform use on both macOS and iPadOS.

